trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty" /> represents a property on a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem" />.

Model properties are associated with an instance of an item, which allows them to have simple Value get/set properties instead of using the more cumbersome GetValue/SetValue mechanism of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor" />.
trans-unit.target: 모델 속성은 항목 인스턴스와 연결되므로 <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor" />의 번거로운 GetValue/SetValue 메커니즘을 사용하는 대신 간단한 값 get/set 속성을 가질 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The value of a <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty> may come from a locally set value, or it may be inherited from somewhere higher up in the element hierarchy.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty>의 값은 설정된 로컬 값에서 제공되거나 요소 계층 구조의 상위 수준에서 상속될 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem.Source*> property of the value returned by <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.Value%2A> to determine the source of the property value.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem.Source*>에서 반환된 값의 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.Value%2A> 속성을 사용하여 속성 값의 소스를 확인할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty" />.

Returns the type that defines this property if <see cref="P:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.IsAttached" /> returns <see langword="true" />; otherwise, returns <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.IsAttached" />에서 <see langword="true" />를 반환하면 이 속성을 정의하는 형식을 반환하고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="null" />을 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.Type" /> or <see langword="null" />.
Returns the attributes declared on this property.
Returns the attributes as an <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection" />.
Clears the local value for the property.
When there is no local value set for the property, a value may be inherited from higher in the property hierarchy.
trans-unit.target: 속성에 대해 설정된 로컬 값이 없는 경우 속성 계층 구조의 상위 수준에서 값이 상속될 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: If you wish to set the value to `null`, call <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.SetValue%2A> instead.
trans-unit.target: 값을 설정 하려는 경우 `null`, 호출 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.SetValue%2A> 대신 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see cref="P:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.Value" /> cast as a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItemCollection" />.
Returns the property value as a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItemCollection" />, or <see langword="null" />.
If the property value is not a collection, this property will return `null`.
trans-unit.target: 경우는 속성 값이 컬렉션을이 속성은 반환 `null`합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns the currently computed value for this property.
trans-unit.target: 이 속성의 현재 계산된 값을 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: Setting a value on this property is the same as calling <see cref="M:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.SetValue(System.Object)" />, but can be used in data binding expressions.
trans-unit.target: 이 속성의 값을 설정하는 것은 <see cref="M:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.SetValue(System.Object)" />를 호출하는 것과 같지만 데이터 바인딩 식에 사용할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns the computed value as an <see cref="T:System.Object" />.
Returns the type converter to use with this property.
trans-unit.target: 이 속성에 사용할 형식 변환기를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter" /> for use with this property.
Underlying type converters are all wrapped so they accept <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem> objects.
trans-unit.target: 기본 형식 변환기는 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem> 개체를 허용하도록 모두 래핑됩니다.

trans-unit.source: When performing a conversion to a particular value, the type converter’s return type is not wrapped.
trans-unit.target: 특정 값으로 변환할 때 형식 변환기의 반환 형식은 래핑되지 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: Type converters that return standard values also return values as <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem> objects.
trans-unit.target: 표준 값을 반환하는 형식 변환기도 값을 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem> 개체로 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns the default value for this property.
If the property does not define a default value, this will return <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 속성에서 기본값을 정의하지 않는 경우 <see langword="null" />이 반환됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns an <see cref="T:System.Object" /> or <see langword="null" />.
Returns <see cref="P:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.Value" /> cast as a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItemDictionary" />.
If the property value is not a dictionary, this property will return <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 속성 값이 사전이 아니면 이 속성에서 <see langword="null" />을 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItemDictionary" /> or <see langword="null" />.
The property to compare with this property.
Determines the equality for properties.
Properties are equal if they have the same name and parent.
<see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="obj" /> is a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty" /> that equals this property; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="obj" />가 이 속성과 동일한 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty" />이면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Serves as a hash function for a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty" />.
Returns a hashcode as an <see cref="T:System.Int32" />.
Determines whether the property represents an attached property from a different type.
trans-unit.target: 속성이 다른 형식의 연결된 속성을 나타내는지 여부를 결정합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the property represents an attached property from a different type; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 속성이 다른 형식의 연결된 속성을 나타내면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the property can be shown in a property window.
trans-unit.target: 속성 창에 속성을 표시할 수 있는지 여부를 결정합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the property can be shown in a property window; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 속성 창에 속성을 표시할 수 있으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the value contained in the property is a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItemCollection" />.
<see langword="true" /> if the value contained in the property is a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItemCollection" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 속성에 포함된 값이 <see langword="true" />이면 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItemCollection" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the value contained in the property is a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItemDictionary" />.
<see langword="true" /> if the value contained in the property is a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Design.Model.ModelItemDictionary" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 속성에 포함된 값이 <see langword="true" />이면 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Design.Model.ModelItemDictionary" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the property is read only.
<see langword="true" /> if the property is read only; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 속성이 읽기 전용이면 <see langword="true" />이고 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the value of the property is set locally.
trans-unit.target: 속성 값이 로컬로 설정되는지 여부를 결정합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the value of the property is set locally; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 속성 값이 로컬로 설정되었으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of this property.
The name of this property.
The first property.
The second property.
Determines whether the properties are equal.
Properties are equal if they have the same name and parent.
<see langword="true" /> if the first property equals the second property; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 첫 번째 속성이 두 번째 속성과 같으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The first property.
The second property.
Determines whether the properties are unequal.
Properties are equal if they have the same name and parent.
<see langword="false" /> if the first property equals the second property; otherwise, <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: 첫 번째 속성이 두 번째 속성과 같으면 <see langword="false" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="true" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns the parent of this property.
Returns the parent of this property as a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Design.Model.ModelItem" />.
Returns the data type of the property.
Returns the <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of the property.
The new value to set.
Sets a local value on a property.
Returns <paramref name="value" /> as a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem" />.
If `value` is not a <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem>, it is wrapped in a <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem>, which is returned to the caller.
It is valid to set `value` to `null`, in which case <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.Value%2A> will be `null`.
trans-unit.target: 설정 하는 데 유효한 `value` 를 `null`있으며이 경우 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.Value%2A> 됩니다 `null`합니다.

trans-unit.source: This is different from calling <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.ClearValue%2A>.
Using this method, the value will not be set on the underlying property until the editing context completes.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드를 사용 하 여 값 수에 설정 하지 않습니다는 기본 속성 편집 컨텍스트 완료 될 때까지 합니다.

trans-unit.source: To update the underlying property immediately, use <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ArgumentAccessor.Setter%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 기본 속성을 즉시 업데이트를 사용 하 여 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ArgumentAccessor.Setter%2A>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns the value set into this property.
Returns the property value as a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem" />, or <see langword="null" />.

A property may return a value that is inherited further up the element hierarchy, in which case this property will return a value whose <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem.Source%2A> is not `this`.
trans-unit.target: 속성 상속 된 값을 반환할 수 위쪽 요소 계층에 있는 경우이 속성 값이 반환 됩니다 인 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem.Source%2A> 않습니다 `this`합니다.

trans-unit.source: If no value has ever been set for the property <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.Value%2A> will return `null`.
trans-unit.target: 속성에 값이 없는 경우 현재까지 설정 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelProperty.Value%2A> 돌아갑니다 `null`합니다.
